          "description": "I am extremely pleased with this place. They offer same-day appointments. The staff is extremely friendly. My x-ray technician was extremely thorough and gentle throughout the entire process. Dr. Reddy performed a detailed examination. She has excellent bedside manner and was very informative. She asked if I had a primary dentist that I usually see and offered to have all of the information, notes, and x-rays sent over. Extremely pleasant experience and would highly recommend!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taVWFrRnNlbUUwY0hWeE9YbHpka0ZQT0dWR1JYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkZUakFsemE0cHVxOXlzdkFPOGVGRXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
