        {
          "username": "Jonny Katz",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "104404337999492736534",
          "user_review_count": 9,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQZvPbRUvW2rxiQ3QN_PkoRg54J1sroTh3jUylV1_b56S9LA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This is by far the best Dental practice I\u2019ve ever experienced and in NYC! Not one to usually enjoy the dentist, Dr. Reddy (and dental assistants) made my visits extremely comforting, professional, one of a kind, painless and something I actually looked forward too! They also give you a x ray and show you scans to provide reasons for potential treatments. Everyone from the front desk to the dentists were very kind and welcoming. It\u2019s the first time in my life I left smiling and happy for taking care of my teeth the proper way. As for billing and reasons for certain services they are 10/10, upfront, clear, not pushy and no upselling! It\u2019s also very convenient that it\u2019s by so many subway stops. I was really surprised in my few visits the last couple of weeks I never once experienced any pain or discomfort. They also make sure any fillings are perfectly fitted before you leave. Dr. Reddy was the first dentist I saw at 209 a year or so ago. I chose to stick with her and I couldn\u2019t have made a better choice! She really cares about the person, the passion for dentistry, the staff and making sure the person leaves with the best quality and experience. If you\u2019re looking for a dentistry that will change the way you think about the dentist, book your appointment (by the way super easy to book appointments too) with Dr. Reddy (or their other talented and caring dentists)! I\u2019m not joking while getting my filling put in I actually said \u201cthis reminds me of the spa\u201d! Fair pricing for the quality as well! 100/100!!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aV2JIZGhOekJmWDFWVVVXbGxSbXh6ZUcweFJHYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmZWbHdhNzBfX1VUUWllRmxzeG0xRGc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-03-03T23:52:26+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Jessica Miller",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "104989826299588753542",
          "user_review_count": 14,
          "user_photo_count": 32,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL66w8v3GSXxfNoxVJd7ndBUJ5L18vl3gVzAG3QmDTp8ndsgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I genuinely enjoy this dentist office. It runs smoothly, and office staff are kind & professional. Dr. Reddy is the best - knowledgeable, skillful & patient. She spends time explaining things in full and cares about her patients. Dainea at the front desk is just as wonderful and equally patient.\n\nToday Dr. Reddy polished up my chipped composite veneer that my previous dentist had done, and mentioned she loves to do cosmetic work. It definitely shows - I left feeling so good about my teeth today. Couldn\u2019t be more grateful for her, her team, and Dainea.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ZeFdsbEZSa1ZIY0dkcVZrRXpXREp1ZFhvNE1VRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmYxWllFRkVHcGdqVkEzWDJudXo4MUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 weeks ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-29T19:49:18+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "bklyn747",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "100890705211766506162",
          "user_review_count": 8,
          "user_photo_count": 7,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVs4aZI5kvfI-ELoD5tOlcKIDduaKYhPXPiVm50c3osb_VGQsa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I recently visited 209 NYC Dental for the first time with my child in December. As a new patient during one of the busiest times of year\u2014when many people rush to use remaining insurance benefits\u2014I wasn\u2019t sure what to expect.\n\nThe check-in process was thorough, and while there was some waiting, this seemed perfectly reasonable given the seasonal rush. When I was asked to pay upfront for my procedure, I inquired about the policy. This practice didn\u2019t surprise me, as I\u2019ve encountered the same approach at other medical providers, including major academic medical centers like Columbia University Irving Medical Center and NewYork-Presbyterian, where payment responsibility is routinely confirmed before appointments.\nWhat truly stood out was the quality of care once we were seen. Dr. Park and her assistant were exceptional with my child\u2014keeping the atmosphere relaxed, engaging her in light conversation, and expertly easing her nerves throughout the visit. Dr. Ifraimov went above and beyond by taking care of an unscheduled procedure for me, saving me from having to return for a follow-up visit. Both experiences were professional, well-organized, and genuinely attentive.\nCommunication was clear at every step, and the treatment exceeded my expectations. This is top-notch dental care delivered with skill and consideration. I\u2019m grateful we found this practice and would confidently recommend it to other families.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOaGFsRkZUaTFWYVZJdGNtNTNjbWswVmtOTlJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlNhalFFTi1VaVItcm53cmk0VkNNRmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "4 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-02-09T21:32:30+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Steven Garcia",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "110316682750957710895",
          "user_review_count": 19,
          "user_photo_count": 2,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWH2kzDTD2VP94xBFVe6QBLEdHc-7hyaGB74v1e3Nzt-DjanqGIMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I visited this clinic recently for an emergency molar extraction after my regular dentist couldn't see me until later in the week. From the moment I called for a same-day appointment, I knew I was in good hands.\n\nThe office is modern and welcoming, and the reception team was incredibly friendly. I was seen quickly by Miriam and Dr. Wang, who were both phenomenal. They were highly professional, educational, and provided a level of comfort I haven\u2019t experienced at a dentist in years.\n\nThe procedure itself was top-tier, completely painless. They kept me informed every step of the way and provided clear post-op instructions. I was blown away that I was headed home within an hour of arriving. The high praise and volume of reviews here are well-deserved; this is easily one of the best dental offices in the city. Thank you to the whole team!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twdWJERkdOVnBwV0hKd1dHdHFNSFJsU2pSd1RFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkpubDFGNVppWHJwWGtqMHRlSjRwTEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-10T12:38:28+00:00"
        },
        {
