          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8cCIJszZvVHLqs2jNTgoKnU3ElEsB96m806ixlZ5PjITZ4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I just had my first visit at this office and it was great! I was seen right away after check in. The entire visit was efficient and the staff were very transparent and helpful throughout. They were not pushy on trying to sell me \u201cextra stuff,\u201d like my old dentist office had done in the past. I had a great check up here at 209.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tObFRFa3hTbXhDU1V0bVdqQm5jM00xU2xKdlRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkNlTEkxSmxCSUtmWjBnc3M1SlJvTHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
