          "description": "I've been a patient of Dr. Park's for a few years, and I couldn't be happier with the care I've received. Her expertise, kindness, and attention to detail make every visit a great experience. Before finding 209 Dental, I was always anxious about going to the dentist. Dr. Park completely changed my experience through her amazing care and kindness. Thanks to her, I no longer fear coming in for cleanings and treatments :)",
